{"tid":661031,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過上天台大叫","createTime":"2018-05-11T07:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T08:10:41.000Z","uid":42509,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"855fc66ec5d823ffe860d09d4d8929496694db7d","tid":661031,"uid":42509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"最近呢個月失去左好多野，女，錢，自尊。<br />\n<br />\n所以尋晚我去左人地屋苑個天台，為左抒發一下情緒<br />\n<br />\n之後我就係度大叫<br />\n<br />\n我：我要攞返我失去既野<br />\n<br />\n之後有條撚樣覆返我<br />\n<br />\n撚樣：去報失啦，仆街<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點算，叫完個人都仲好失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f108849e6fa7bfdcea29bb9a7591c7b52f5d4df","tid":661031,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"Thx for sharing"},{"pid":"0aec7bb1d1367b3bdf0b6b47a62f3d937da60a98","tid":661031,"uid":92611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"人地屋苑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解唔去自己屋苑"},{"pid":"306f33650c9eaccfaaa698cb42b653d81e130a4f","tid":661031,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd761e634b65cef03f8cebe145d2a02e038fd02","tid":661031,"uid":56157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0aec7bb1d1367b3bdf0b6b47a62f3d937da60a98","tid":661031,"uid":92611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"人地屋苑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解唔去自己屋苑"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"係自己屋苑鄰居認得你以為你係癡線<br />\n(可能樓主真係癡線)"},{"pid":"d7ee349ced383e92f510cd834003e7e07e4ddb91","tid":661031,"uid":92611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd761e634b65cef03f8c